title: Wolverine 001 (2014) (Scanbro) All New Marvel NOW
description:
CBZ | English | 23 pages

Wolverine #1 (Volume 6)
Written by Paul Cornell
Pencilled by Ryan Stegman
Inked by Mark Morales
Coloured by David Curiel
Lettered by VC's Cory Petit

WOLVERINE NO MORE?

After the events of KILLABLE, Wolverine has something to prove. Before he can take on Sabretooth again, he'll need to build himself back up, get better and stronger than he's ever been...but it's not as easy as he thought, and he'll soon find himself turning to other means of revenge when the normal channels don't seem to be working fast enough. Can he fight back his demons, or is this the beginning of a Wolverine who's gone to the dark side?

PARENTAL ADVISORY

--------

This is an early scan of the Wolverine. It is not in high quality. If you want a high quality release then you have three options: got to your local comic books store and pick it up from there on the fifth of February, buy it digitally from comixology or the marvel store, and finally pirate the digital rip which should be available sometime after the fifth of February.
